('how-to-choose-lipstick',
'How to Choose the Right Lipstick for Your Skin Tone',
'Finding the perfect lipstick shade can transform your entire look. Learn how to match lipstick to your skin tone, undertone, and occasion for a flawless finish every time.',
'<h2>Why the Right Lipstick Matters</h2><p>Your lipstick is the finishing touch to any makeup look. The wrong shade can wash you out, while the right one makes you glow. At Shree Ambika Beauty Shop, Mumbai, we have helped thousands of women find their perfect match since 2001.</p><h2>Know Your Undertone</h2><p><strong>Cool undertones</strong> (pink or bluish veins): Go for berry, rose, mauve, or deep plum shades.<br><strong>Warm undertones</strong> (greenish veins): Try coral, peach, brick red, or terracotta.<br><strong>Neutral undertones</strong>: You are lucky — almost every shade works!</p><h2>Best Shades by Skin Tone</h2><ul><li><strong>Fair skin:</strong> Nudes, pinks, light coral</li><li><strong>Medium skin:</strong> Rose, mauve, peach, berry</li><li><strong>Dusky skin:</strong> Deep red, wine, plum, brick</li><li><strong>Dark skin:</strong> Bold reds, deep berry, copper</li></ul><h2>Finish Matters Too</h2><p><strong>Matte:</strong> Long-lasting, bold. Best for evenings.<br><strong>Glossy:</strong> Fuller-looking lips. Great for day wear.<br><strong>Satin:</strong> Best of both — comfortable all day.</p><h2>Top Picks Available at Our Store</h2><p>We stock Lakme, SUGAR, Maybelline, RENEE, and 50+ brands. Visit our store in Dahisar, Mumbai or WhatsApp Vinod at +918291455297 to order.</p>',
'Makeup', ARRAY['lipstick','makeup tips','skin tone','beauty guide','Mumbai beauty','Lakme lipstick','SUGAR cosmetics'], 'How to Choose the Right Lipstick for Your Skin Tone | Mumbai Beauty Guide', 'Learn how to choose the perfect lipstick for your skin tone. Expert tips from Shree Ambika Beauty Shop, Mumbai — 25+ years of beauty expertise.', 5, true),

('how-to-select-foundation',
'How to Select the Right Foundation — Complete Guide for Indian Skin',
'Foundation is the base of all makeup. Choosing the wrong shade or formula can make your look cakey or mismatched. This guide helps you pick the perfect foundation for Indian skin tones.',
'<h2>Why Foundation Matching is Tricky</h2><p>Indian skin has warm, golden undertones that many international foundations miss. At Shree Ambika Beauty Shop, Mumbai, we stock foundations specifically designed for Indian and South Asian skin tones.</p><h2>Step 1: Find Your Undertone</h2><p><strong>Warm:</strong> Yellow, peachy undertones — look for foundations with "warm" or "golden" in the name.<br><strong>Cool:</strong> Pinkish or rosy — choose "cool" or "porcelain" shades.<br><strong>Neutral:</strong> Mix of both — labelled "neutral" or "beige".</p><h2>Step 2: Choose Your Coverage</h2><ul><li><strong>Light/Sheer:</strong> For daily, natural looks. BB creams work great.</li><li><strong>Medium:</strong> Covers blemishes but looks skin-like.</li><li><strong>Full coverage:</strong> Ideal for events, weddings, photography.</li></ul><h2>Step 3: Formula for Your Skin Type</h2><p><strong>Oily skin:</strong> Matte, oil-control, long-wear formula.<br><strong>Dry skin:</strong> Hydrating, dewy, serum foundation.<br><strong>Combination:</strong> Semi-matte or satin finish.</p><h2>Best Brands We Recommend</h2><p>Lakme Skin Tint, Maybelline Fit Me, SUGAR Ace of Face, Huda Beauty — all available at our Mumbai store. WhatsApp Vinod: +918291455297.</p>',
'Makeup', ARRAY['foundation','makeup','Indian skin tone','beauty guide','Mumbai makeup','Lakme foundation'], 'How to Choose Foundation for Indian Skin | Shree Ambika Beauty Shop', 'Complete guide to selecting the right foundation for Indian skin. Coverage, undertone, and formula tips from Mumbai beauty experts since 2001.', 6, true),

('how-to-choose-hair-colour',
'How to Choose the Right Hair Colour for Your Skin Tone',
'The right hair colour can brighten your complexion and boost your confidence. The wrong one can look harsh. Here is how to choose wisely based on your skin tone and lifestyle.',
'<h2>Hair Colour and Skin Tone — The Connection</h2><p>Your natural complexion is the best guide to hair colour. As Mumbai''s trusted beauty shop since 2001, we have helped thousands choose colours they love.</p><h2>Best Hair Colours by Skin Tone</h2><h3>Fair Skin</h3><p>Blonde, honey brown, strawberry, light chestnut. Avoid jet black as it can look harsh.</p><h3>Medium/Wheatish Skin</h3><p>Warm browns, caramel, auburn, chocolate. These add warmth and complement beautifully.</p><h3>Dusky/Dark Skin</h3><p>Deep burgundy, copper, mahogany, warm black. Avoid very light shades — they can look unnatural.</p><h2>Permanent vs Temporary Colour</h2><p><strong>Permanent:</strong> Lasts 4–6 weeks, better grey coverage.<br><strong>Semi-permanent:</strong> Fades gradually, less damaging.<br><strong>Temporary:</strong> Washes out in 1–2 shampoos — great for experimenting.</p><h2>Hair Colour Care Tips</h2><ul><li>Use colour-protect shampoo and conditioner</li><li>Deep condition weekly</li><li>Avoid hot water washing</li><li>Wella, Streax, L''Oreal Casting available at our store</li></ul><p>Order now on WhatsApp: +918291455297 from Shree Ambika Beauty Shop, Dahisar Mumbai.</p>',
'Hair Care', ARRAY['hair colour','hair care','skin tone','beauty tips','Wella','Streax','Mumbai hair care'], 'How to Choose Hair Colour for Your Skin Tone | Mumbai Beauty Guide', 'Find the perfect hair colour for your skin tone. Expert advice from Shree Ambika Beauty Shop Mumbai — 500+ products, same day delivery.', 5, true),

('how-to-buy-skincare-products',
'How to Buy Skincare Products — Know Your Skin Type First',
'Walking into a beauty store without knowing your skin type is like shopping for shoes without knowing your size. This guide helps you identify your skin type and choose the right products.',
'<h2>The 5 Skin Types</h2><p>Before buying any skincare product, identify your skin type. Here is a simple test: wash your face, wait 1 hour without applying anything, then observe.</p><h3>1. Normal Skin</h3><p>No excess oil or dryness. Lucky you! Focus on maintenance with gentle cleanser, moisturiser, and SPF.</p><h3>2. Oily Skin</h3><p>Shiny forehead, nose, and chin (T-zone). Look for oil-free, non-comedogenic, gel-based products. Niacinamide and salicylic acid are your friends.</p><h3>3. Dry Skin</h3><p>Tight, flaky, or rough feeling. Choose cream-based, hydrating products with hyaluronic acid, ceramides, and shea butter.</p><h3>4. Combination Skin</h3><p>Oily T-zone, dry cheeks. Use gentle balancing products. Gel moisturisers work well.</p><h3>5. Sensitive Skin</h3><p>Redness, reactions easily. Avoid fragrance, alcohol, and harsh acids. Look for fragrance-free, dermatologist-tested products.</p><h2>The Basic Skincare Routine</h2><ol><li>Cleanser</li><li>Toner</li><li>Serum (targeted concern)</li><li>Moisturiser</li><li>SPF (morning only)</li></ol><h2>Best Skincare Brands We Stock</h2><p>Plum, Mamaearth, Biotique, Pilgrim, WOW, Lotus, Neutrogena — all original at Shree Ambika Beauty Shop, Dahisar Mumbai. WhatsApp: +918291455297.</p>',
'Skin Care', ARRAY['skincare','skin type','beauty guide','skincare routine','Mumbai skincare','Plum','Mamaearth'], 'How to Buy Skincare Products — Know Your Skin Type | Mumbai Beauty', 'Learn to identify your skin type and buy the right skincare products. Expert guide from Shree Ambika Beauty Shop, Mumbai — 100% original products.', 7, true),

('how-to-spot-original-products',
'How to Spot Original Beauty Products — Avoid Fake Cosmetics',
'Fake beauty products are everywhere in India. They can damage your skin, cause allergies, and waste your money. Learn how to identify genuine products before buying.',
'<h2>The Problem with Fake Cosmetics</h2><p>Counterfeit beauty products are made with unregulated ingredients — some contain heavy metals, bacteria, or cheap fillers. In Mumbai alone, fake products are widely sold in local markets.</p><h2>7 Ways to Identify Original Products</h2><ol><li><strong>Check the packaging:</strong> Original products have clear, well-printed labels. Blurry print, spelling errors, or uneven fonts are red flags.</li><li><strong>Look for batch codes:</strong> Every original product has a manufacturing date, expiry date, and batch number.</li><li><strong>Verify on brand website:</strong> Many brands like Lakme, Maybelline offer authenticity checks on their websites.</li><li><strong>Check the seal:</strong> Tamper-evident seals, holograms, and shrink wrap should be intact.</li><li><strong>Smell test:</strong> Fake products often smell chemical or different from the original.</li><li><strong>Texture check:</strong> If the texture, colour, or consistency looks off, be suspicious.</li><li><strong>Buy from trusted stores:</strong> Always buy from authorized retailers like Shree Ambika Beauty Shop, Dahisar Mumbai.</li></ol><h2>Why Buy from Shree Ambika Beauty Shop?</h2><p>We have been serving Mumbai since 2001. All our products are sourced directly from brands and authorized distributors. 100% original guarantee. WhatsApp Vinod: +918291455297.</p>',
'Beauty Tips', ARRAY['original products','fake cosmetics','authentic beauty','Mumbai beauty shop','100% original','buying guide'], 'How to Spot Original Beauty Products — Avoid Fake Cosmetics India', 'Learn to identify genuine beauty products and avoid fakes. Expert guide from Shree Ambika Beauty Shop Mumbai — 100% original since 2001.', 5, true),

('how-to-build-beauty-kit',
'How to Build Your Complete Beauty Kit — Essential Products for Every Woman',
'Whether you are a beginner or a beauty enthusiast, having the right products in your kit makes all the difference. Here is everything you need for a complete beauty kit.',
'<h2>The Essential Beauty Kit</h2><p>You do not need 100 products. You need the right ones. At Shree Ambika Beauty Shop Mumbai, we help customers build practical kits that work for their lifestyle.</p><h2>Skincare Essentials</h2><ul><li>Face wash / cleanser</li><li>Toner or micellar water</li><li>Moisturiser with SPF</li><li>Night cream or serum</li><li>Eye cream (if concerned about dark circles)</li></ul><h2>Makeup Basics</h2><ul><li>BB cream or lightweight foundation</li><li>Concealer (one shade lighter)</li><li>Compact powder</li><li>Kajal / eyeliner</li><li>Mascara</li><li>2 lipsticks (one nude, one bold)</li><li>Blush or bronzer</li></ul><h2>Hair Care Essentials</h2><ul><li>Shampoo for your hair type</li><li>Conditioner</li><li>Hair serum or oil</li><li>Heat protectant (if you use styling tools)</li></ul><h2>Tools</h2><ul><li>Makeup brushes (foundation, blush, eye)</li><li>Makeup sponge / beauty blender</li><li>Eyelash curler</li><li>Tweezers</li></ul><p>Build your complete beauty kit from Shree Ambika Beauty Shop. Same day delivery in Mumbai. WhatsApp: +918291455297.</p>',
'Beauty Tips', ARRAY['beauty kit','makeup essentials','skincare routine','beauty products','Mumbai beauty','beginner makeup'], 'How to Build Your Complete Beauty Kit | Shree Ambika Beauty Shop Mumbai', 'Essential products for your beauty kit — skincare, makeup, and haircare basics. Shop at Shree Ambika Beauty Shop Mumbai with same day delivery.', 6, true),

('best-skincare-routine-mumbai',
'Best Skincare Routine for Mumbai''s Humid Weather',
'Mumbai''s humidity, pollution, and sun damage require a special skincare approach. Here is a dermatologist-approved routine tailored for Mumbai''s unique climate.',
'<h2>Why Mumbai Skin Needs Special Care</h2><p>Mumbai''s tropical climate — high humidity, strong UV rays, and pollution — creates a perfect storm for oily skin, clogged pores, and sun damage. A Mumbai-specific routine is essential.</p><h2>Morning Routine for Mumbai Skin</h2><ol><li><strong>Gentle cleanser:</strong> Remove sweat and overnight oil without stripping moisture.</li><li><strong>Vitamin C serum:</strong> Fights pollution damage and brightens skin.</li><li><strong>Lightweight moisturiser:</strong> Gel-based for humid weather.</li><li><strong>SPF 50+ sunscreen:</strong> Non-negotiable in Mumbai. Reapply every 2 hours if outdoors.</li></ol><h2>Evening Routine</h2><ol><li><strong>Double cleanse:</strong> Micellar water first, then face wash to remove pollution and makeup.</li><li><strong>Niacinamide serum:</strong> Controls oil and minimises pores.</li><li><strong>Night moisturiser:</strong> Slightly richer than day cream.</li></ol><h2>Weekly Treatments</h2><ul><li>Exfoliate 2x per week (AHA/BHA)</li><li>Sheet mask or clay mask</li><li>Facial oil massage before bed once a week</li></ul><p>Shop all products at Shree Ambika Beauty Shop, Dahisar Mumbai or order on WhatsApp: +918291455297. Same day delivery in Mumbai.</p>',
'Skin Care', ARRAY['skincare routine','Mumbai skincare','humidity skincare','SPF','oily skin','pollution skincare','Indian skincare'], 'Best Skincare Routine for Mumbai''s Humid Weather | Expert Guide 2024', 'Dermatologist-approved skincare routine for Mumbai''s humid climate. Shop original skincare at Shree Ambika Beauty Shop, Dahisar Mumbai.', 7, true),

('hair-care-tips-indian-women',
'Complete Hair Care Guide for Indian Women — Strong, Shiny Hair Naturally',
'Indian hair has unique needs. Learn the best hair care routine, oiling tips, and product recommendations for healthy, strong, and shiny hair from roots to tips.',
'<h2>Understanding Indian Hair</h2><p>Indian hair is typically thick, dark, and coarse — but also prone to frizz, dryness at tips, and oily scalp. The right routine makes a dramatic difference.</p><h2>The Oil Massage — India''s Best Kept Secret</h2><p>Regular scalp massage with warm oil improves circulation and strengthens roots. Best oils:</p><ul><li><strong>Coconut oil:</strong> Penetrates shaft, reduces breakage</li><li><strong>Castor oil:</strong> Thickens hair, fights hair fall</li><li><strong>Onion oil:</strong> Stimulates regrowth</li><li><strong>Argan oil:</strong> Adds shine and tames frizz</li></ul><h2>Weekly Hair Care Routine</h2><ol><li>Oil massage 2 hours before washing</li><li>Shampoo with sulphate-free formula</li><li>Condition mid-length to tips only</li><li>Cold water rinse for shine</li><li>Air dry or use heat protectant before blow drying</li></ol><h2>Common Mistakes to Avoid</h2><ul><li>Washing hair daily — strips natural oils</li><li>Rubbing hair roughly with towel</li><li>Applying conditioner on scalp</li><li>Using hot water for washing</li></ul><p>We stock Wella, Streax, Mamaearth, WOW, L''Oreal hair care at our Mumbai store. WhatsApp: +918291455297.</p>',
'Hair Care', ARRAY['hair care','Indian hair','hair tips','hair fall','hair growth','oiling hair','Mumbai hair care'], 'Complete Hair Care Guide for Indian Women | Shree Ambika Beauty Shop', 'Expert hair care tips for Indian women — oiling, shampooing, and styling. Shop hair care products at Shree Ambika Beauty Shop Mumbai.', 6, true),

('makeup-for-beginners',
'Makeup for Beginners — Step-by-Step Guide to Your First Makeup Routine',
'Starting with makeup can feel overwhelming. This beginner-friendly guide walks you through every step — from prepping your skin to finishing touches — with product recommendations.',
'<h2>Before You Start</h2><p>Good makeup starts with good skincare. Always moisturise and apply SPF before makeup. This creates a smooth base and protects your skin.</p><h2>Step-by-Step Beginner Makeup</h2><h3>Step 1: Primer (optional)</h3><p>Helps makeup last longer and minimises pores. Apply a pea-sized amount all over face.</p><h3>Step 2: Foundation or BB Cream</h3><p>For beginners, start with BB cream or a light foundation. Blend with a damp beauty sponge.</p><h3>Step 3: Concealer</h3><p>Apply under eyes and on any blemishes. Pat gently — do not rub.</p><h3>Step 4: Set with Powder</h3><p>A light dusting of compact powder sets your base and controls oil throughout the day.</p><h3>Step 5: Eye Makeup</h3><p>Start with kajal on the waterline — simple but impactful. Add mascara for definition.</p><h3>Step 6: Blush</h3><p>Smile and apply to the apples of your cheeks. Blend upward toward temples.</p><h3>Step 7: Lip Colour</h3><p>Start with a nude or your-lips-but-better shade for daytime. Bold lips for evenings.</p><h2>Essential Beginner Products</h2><p>Lakme, Maybelline, SUGAR — all beginner-friendly and affordable, available at Shree Ambika Beauty Shop, Dahisar Mumbai. WhatsApp Vinod: +918291455297 to order.</p>',
'Makeup', ARRAY['beginner makeup','makeup tutorial','first makeup','beauty guide','Mumbai beauty','step by step makeup'], 'Makeup for Beginners — Step-by-Step Guide | Shree Ambika Beauty Shop Mumbai', 'Complete beginner makeup guide with product recommendations. Shop affordable, original makeup at Shree Ambika Beauty Shop, Dahisar Mumbai.', 8, true),

('perfume-guide-how-to-choose',
'How to Choose the Right Perfume — Complete Fragrance Guide for India',
'Fragrance is the most personal part of your beauty routine. The right perfume becomes your signature. Learn how to choose a fragrance that suits your personality, skin, and occasion.',
'<h2>Understanding Fragrance Notes</h2><p>Every perfume has three layers of scent that unfold over time:</p><ul><li><strong>Top notes:</strong> First impression — citrus, bergamot, light florals. Lasts 15-30 minutes.</li><li><strong>Middle/Heart notes:</strong> The core — rose, jasmine, lavender. Lasts 2-4 hours.</li><li><strong>Base notes:</strong> The lasting memory — musk, sandalwood, vanilla. Lasts 6+ hours.</li></ul><h2>Fragrance Families</h2><ul><li><strong>Floral:</strong> Rose, jasmine, lily — feminine, romantic. Perfect for weddings.</li><li><strong>Woody:</strong> Sandalwood, cedar, oud — warm, sensual. Great for evenings.</li><li><strong>Citrus/Fresh:</strong> Lemon, bergamot — clean, energetic. Ideal for daily use.</li><li><strong>Oriental:</strong> Amber, spices, vanilla — rich and exotic. Best for winters and evenings.</li></ul><h2>How to Test Perfume</h2><ol><li>Spray on wrist, not paper strip</li><li>Wait 10 minutes — let it dry down</li><li>Smell again — this is the real scent on your skin</li><li>Do not rub wrists together — it breaks the molecules</li></ol><h2>How to Make Perfume Last Longer</h2><p>Apply on pulse points — wrists, neck, behind ears, inside elbows. Moisturise skin first for better longevity. Store in cool, dark place.</p><p>We stock 100+ perfumes from top brands. Shop at Shree Ambika Beauty Shop, Dahisar Mumbai or WhatsApp: +918291455297.</p>',
'Perfumes', ARRAY['perfume guide','fragrance','how to choose perfume','perfume tips','Mumbai perfume','fragrance notes','oud'], 'How to Choose the Right Perfume — Complete Fragrance Guide | Mumbai', 'Expert fragrance guide — understand notes, choose by personality and occasion. Shop 100+ original perfumes at Shree Ambika Beauty Shop Mumbai.', 6, true);
